<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="de">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>ECO‑MARKT – Modul</title>

<style>
    body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        background: #e8f5e9;
        color: #1b5e20;
        margin: 40px;
    }
    .box {
        background: #ffffff;
        padding: 25px;
        border-radius: 10px;
        box-shadow: 0 0 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
    }
    h1 {
        font-size: 2rem;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .pulse {
        animation: pulse 1.4s infinite;
    }
    @keyframes pulse {
        0% { opacity: 0.4; }
        50% { opacity: 1; }
        100% { opacity: 0.4; }
    }
</style>
</head>

<body>
<div class="box pulse">
    <h1>ECO‑MARKT – LIVE</h1>
    <p>Dieses Modul ist aktiv und bereit für Erweiterungen.</p>
    <p>Status: <strong>ONLINE</strong></p>
</div>
</body>
</html>
